reviewText: I bought this as a gift for my Dad and he was really excited. I've never seen the movies but I imagine this is a great gift for anyone who is a collector of such films.

These two films from Roan make for a great double feature.  This DVD is one of Roan's better releases.  Both films are complete and with all original titles.  The prints are a little worn but are splice-free.
i will never buy an alpha product again. this is very poor quailty as are all the alphas i have bought. this is a good movie, but the picture is so poor it is not worth it..

Well worth the money. These two lesser known horror features from the forties are just the thing to satisfy those looking for vintage chills.
Fun movies, well presented.
Lets see more like this on DVD.
